                Mr. Davies
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-26b2d104-b0cc-4040-83d6-d6488903700c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-07-05/debates/14099432-7bb3-4947-af53-3453cd8ff233/Korea#contribution-26b2d104-b0cc-4040-83d6-d6488903700c">
