<p class="">Let the hon. Gentleman say now if he thinks that any right hon. or hon. Member on this side of the House wants war. Answer that question. Say "Yes" or "No."</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-47d538fd-55c5-47c0-b2b0-c91f13385e3d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
