<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-7e864e62-6bc0-41c5-ac7c-aa61e49db0f4'>
            
<p class="">Resolved:</p><p class=""> <blockquote><q>"That this House fully supports the action taken by His Majesty's Government in conformity with their obligations under the United Nations Charter, in helping to resist the unprovoked aggression against the Republic of Korea."</q></blockquote></p>
        </div>
